252
00:31:22.422 --> 00:31:23.840
Mengapa anda berfikir begitu?

253
00:31:26.342 --> 00:31:27.635
Sang-ung<i>...</i>

254
00:31:30.430 --> 00:31:31.806
Dia tidak pandai mengira.

255
